Otherwise, this could be done in a single forEach:




        Suggested change











                    particleEmitters.forEach(x -> updateParticleData(x, delta));



                    particleEmitters.forEach(x -> {



                        updateParticleEmitters(x, delta);



                        updateParticleData(x, delta);



                    });

